[gd_scene load_steps=54 format=3]

; SNOW — Wintry peak for a ~1.5m penguin.
; Landmarks: Arrival Clearing (signpost), Pine Forest, Frozen Lake
;   (very_slippery) with ice-cap islands + snow bank ring, Chill Cabin
;   (interior: rug, bed, fireplace, torch), Chairlift (two wood_dark
;   towers + cable), Mountain Stepping Path up the back of the lake to
;   a Peak Plateau, Ski-Slope Slide (very_slippery) returning to spawn.
; Secrets: Igloo cave (1up + 4 coins), Cabin attic via stacked crates
;   (cap_metal on roof), Snowman (visible star beside it), Undercabin
;   crawlspace (red coin).
; Tiers: clearing → cabin/lake → peak.
; Content: 13 enemies, 30 yellow + 8 red coins, 2 stars, 2 1ups, 1 metal cap.

